== The last supper ==

The article says that the last supper is believed to be a passover seder. But this is only true for the synoptic gospels (Luke, John, Mark). In John (see John 13) the last supper clearly takes place before the first day of passover.  <span style="font-size: smaller;" class="autosigned">â€” Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/92.225.172.135|92.225.172.135]] ([[User talk:92.225.172.135|talk]]) 13:35, 25 June 2012 (UTC)</span><!-- Template:Unsigned IP --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->

== Messianic Judaism vs Hebrew Christianity ==

[[Messianic Judaism]] is not the same thing has [[Hebrew Christian Movement|Hebrew Christianity]]. Please do not continue to make this change. It is not your's to decide whether Messianic Jews (who consider themselves to be Jews) are actually Jews or not. Nor is it appropriate for you to confuse terms when there is a clear distinction. [[User:ReformedArsenal|ReformedArsenal]] ([[User talk:ReformedArsenal|talk]]) 19:21, 7 November 2012 (UTC)
